Binary files such as `app/src/main/res/mipmap-hdpi/ic_launcher.png` cannot be generated as raw code. Please provide a description of the desired icon or use image design tools to create the launcher asset. For Android apps, it's recommended to use `ImageAsset Studio` in Android Studio to generate launcher icons. Alternatively, supply a scalable vector graphic (SVG) or detailed specification (e.g., icon shape, color, dog theme) for conversion into PNG resources at multiple densities.